universal preferences
=====
open last file(s) on start
default cols for a new list
    add/remove/change order
    only applies to new files
default from, to, statii
    add/edit/remove
    only applies to new files
show/hide toolbar

document properties
=====
current file's from, to, statii
    add new
    remove existing if not assigned
    edit existing
current file's cols
    add/remove/change order
    cannot remove "done" and "title"
